org.jungrapht.visualization.layout.model

Class AggregateLayoutModel<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jungrapht.visualization.layout.model.AggregateLayoutModel<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the vertex type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function<V,Point>, LayoutChange.Producer, LayoutStateChange.Producer, LayoutVertexPositionChange.Listener<V>, LayoutVertexPositionChange.Producer<V>, LayoutModel<V>

    public class AggregateLayoutModel<V>
extends Object
implements LayoutModel<V>
    A Layout implementation that combines multiple other layouts so that they may be manipulated as one layout. The relaxer thread will step each layout in sequence.
    Author:
    Tom Nelson
